channel.title: Comments on: New Internet Mini-series: The West Side

item.title: By: Chris
item.dc:creator: Chris
item.description: I saw this earlier today when it was linked from FresHDV. The only thing I can say is that I was BLOWN AWAY! Please send Ryan my congratulations (I'll be commenting on his site too). The concept is fantastic and amazingly executed. I'm looking forward to more.
